287
00:19:56,230 --> 00:19:58,230
how come you can't even get a girl?

288
00:20:01,230 --> 00:20:02,920
I was working on it.

289
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:05,560
And then you cut me off.

290
00:20:06,230 --> 00:20:07,520
Y'all wait here for a sec.

291
00:20:07,520 --> 00:20:08,580
I'll go for a check.

292
00:20:08,590 --> 00:20:10,990
You can't leave until everything's clear.

293
00:20:20,760 --> 00:20:22,690
You haven't given me an answer yet.

294
00:20:25,310 --> 00:20:26,280
Zhou Siyue,

295
00:20:27,070 --> 00:20:28,280
I'm sorry.

296
00:20:29,470 --> 00:20:32,590
I'm not planning on a relationship, now.

297
00:20:36,520 --> 00:20:37,680
well, you...

298
00:20:38,590 --> 00:20:40,050
you sure can hold a grudge.

299
00:20:42,190 --> 00:20:43,000
Fine,

300
00:20:44,400 --> 00:20:45,730
I'll be waiting for you.

301
00:20:47,310 --> 00:20:49,190
I'll wait for your answer.

302
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:52,710
Xianxian.

303
00:20:54,430 --> 00:20:55,470
why are you here?

304
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:57,040
Su.

305
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:02,310
Mr. Su, what brings you here?

306
00:21:02,830 --> 00:21:03,830
You know them?

307
00:21:04,470 --> 00:21:05,600
They're my friends.

308
00:21:06,920 --> 00:21:07,710
Here.

309
00:21:09,640 --> 00:21:10,430
Thank you.

310
00:21:10,430 --> 00:21:12,430
That's it. You can leave now.

311
00:21:12,430 --> 00:21:13,560
Don't do that again.

312
00:21:14,160 --> 00:21:15,560
Mr. Su, see you then.

313
00:21:15,800 --> 00:21:16,800
Good work.

314
00:21:19,560 --> 00:21:21,110
Why are you here?

315
00:21:22,230 --> 00:21:23,520
The contest starts tomorrow.

316
00:21:23,520 --> 00:21:26,450
I'm here to check the procedures with the organizer.

317
00:21:26,710 --> 00:21:27,950
Are you going back to the hotel?

318
00:21:27,950 --> 00:21:29,080
I can give you a ride.

319
00:21:29,310 --> 00:21:30,230
Sure.

320
00:21:30,640 --> 00:21:31,560
Thank you.

321
00:21:44,950 --> 00:21:46,040
Xianxian,

322
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:48,190
your mom called me the other day.

323
00:21:48,190 --> 00:21:49,710
She asked me to take good care of you,

324
00:21:49,710 --> 00:21:51,520
since we are both in the Huai City now.

325
00:21:51,520 --> 00:21:53,000
I'm a little busy these days,

326
00:21:53,000 --> 00:21:55,200
when I'm done, I'll take you out for fun.

327
00:21:56,640 --> 00:21:58,190
Mr. Su, you're so busy,

328
00:21:59,560 --> 00:22:02,620
maybe we should forget about these social courtesies.

329
00:22:05,230 --> 00:22:06,760
That's where you're wrong.

330
00:22:07,160 --> 00:22:09,290
For me, Xianxian was never a courtesy.

331
00:22:09,590 --> 00:22:11,590
She always sees me as a brother, too.

332
00:22:13,190 --> 00:22:14,110
Does she?

333
00:22:14,590 --> 00:22:16,990
Then how come I have never heard her mention

334
00:22:17,310 --> 00:22:18,510
you, her big brother?

335
00:22:23,830 --> 00:22:24,880
Maybe it's because you two

336
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:26,230
were never that close?

337
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:30,880
It's no wonder that you didn't know.

338
00:22:31,070 --> 00:22:33,040
Of course Xianxian wouldn't tell you.

339
00:22:33,040 --> 00:22:35,230
She wouldn't tell anything to a stranger.

340
00:22:35,230 --> 00:22:37,470
Even if she doesn't tell me anything,

341
00:22:38,070 --> 00:22:39,640
I know what she likes,

342
00:22:39,830 --> 00:22:41,090
and what she dislikes.

343
00:22:59,350 --> 00:23:00,230
Xianxian,

344
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:02,280
I want to talk to you,

345
00:23:02,640 --> 00:23:04,040
about the comic book app.

346
00:23:04,760 --> 00:23:05,800
What is it?

347
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:09,300
Do you mind giving us a minute?

348
00:23:12,280 --> 00:23:14,160
It's not a secret.

349
00:23:14,520 --> 00:23:16,120
Can't you talk in front of me?

350
00:23:18,800 --> 00:23:21,160
It's okay, Su. Go ahead.

351
00:23:22,590 --> 00:23:24,470
Director Zhang of the comic book company

352
00:23:24,470 --> 00:23:26,880
saw your works on your Weibo, and liked them very much.

353
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:28,520
He's having a dinner tomorrow,

354
00:23:28,520 --> 00:23:30,190
and wants to sign the contract with you in person.

355
00:23:30,190 --> 00:23:32,560
That's great. Thank you so much, Su.

356
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:33,590
I didn't do much.

357
00:23:33,590 --> 00:23:34,850
I just introduced you.

358
00:23:35,110 --> 00:23:36,950
I'll take you shopping for some clothes tomorrow.

359
00:23:36,950 --> 00:23:38,680
It's better to dress formally.

360
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:41,470
What's wrong with her clothes?

361
00:23:47,280 --> 00:23:48,350
It's okay, Su.

362
00:23:48,830 --> 00:23:50,040
I have clothes.

363
00:23:50,350 --> 00:23:51,190
Don't worry.

364
00:23:52,760 --> 00:23:55,190
Okay then, I'll go with you tomorrow.

365
00:23:55,430 --> 00:23:56,560
Don't be nervous.

366
00:23:58,160 --> 00:23:59,760
Ding Xian won't be nervous.

367
00:24:00,190 --> 00:24:01,790
You don't know her very well.

368
00:24:07,830 --> 00:24:09,190
I'll see you then.

369
00:24:16,760 --> 00:24:17,760
Zhou Siyue,

370
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:20,070
I have told you,

371
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:23,560
stay away from Xianxian.

372
00:24:25,280 --> 00:24:26,680
I have told you too,

373
00:24:27,590 --> 00:24:29,400
I won't let go.

374
00:24:39,040 --> 00:24:41,170
So that's all for today's discussion,

375
00:24:41,520 --> 00:24:43,470
I hope that in the contest,

376
00:24:43,800 --> 00:24:45,230
we'll all have a good performance.

377
00:24:45,230 --> 00:24:46,310
Thank you all.

378
00:24:52,430 --> 00:24:53,400
Awake now?

379
00:24:56,470 --> 00:24:57,760
You took notes?

380
00:24:58,830 --> 00:25:00,040
Good for you.

381
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:02,350
Career, love,

382
00:25:02,680 --> 00:25:03,640
acing in both.

383
00:25:07,950 --> 00:25:09,400
Look at him,

384
00:25:09,560 --> 00:25:11,160
what a social butterfly.

385
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:13,070
Talking to everyone.

386
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:19,160
Come on, it's none of your business.

387
00:25:20,280 --> 00:25:21,190
Let's go.

388
00:25:21,800 --> 00:25:22,930
Where are you going?

389
00:25:25,760 --> 00:25:26,920
Comic-Con.

390
00:25:27,760 --> 00:25:29,090
Maybe you shouldn't go.

391
00:25:30,830 --> 00:25:31,710
Why?

392
00:25:32,280 --> 00:25:34,010
Because Xianxian is not there.

393
00:25:35,070 --> 00:25:37,070
How do you know that she's not there?

394
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:38,800
I asked Lou Feng and she told me.

395
00:25:39,830 --> 00:25:40,830
Then where is she?

396
00:25:44,640 --> 00:25:45,590
She's...

397
00:25:45,830 --> 00:25:48,760
she's taken back to the hotel by Su Bocong.

398
00:25:52,760 --> 00:25:55,310
Xianxian, how was your show today?

399
00:25:55,680 --> 00:25:56,560
It went well.

400
00:25:56,710 --> 00:25:58,310
And there were a lot of people.

401
00:25:58,310 --> 00:25:59,440
I finished just now.

402
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:02,000
So you haven't eaten all day?

403
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:05,320
- I'm used to it. I'm not hungry. - Ding Xian!

404
00:26:14,590 --> 00:26:16,250
Why didn't you answer my call?

405
00:26:16,950 --> 00:26:18,400
My cell phone is dead.

406
00:26:20,110 --> 00:26:23,070
Weren't you at the academic conference?

407
00:26:23,230 --> 00:26:24,950
Why are you back so soon?

408
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:26,560
It's over.

409
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:29,090
Don't you have a speech to prepare?

410
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:31,310
I pulled an all-nighter and finished it last night.

411
00:26:31,310 --> 00:26:32,920
Then you should go back to your room and catch some sleep.

412
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:34,250
What are you doing here?

413
00:26:36,160 --> 00:26:37,830
I wanna see you.

414
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:44,640
Mr. Zhou, you are really everywhere.

415
00:26:44,830 --> 00:26:45,950
Can't seem to lose you.

416
00:26:45,950 --> 00:26:46,950
Right back at you.

417
00:26:47,710 --> 00:26:48,590
Mr. Su.

418
00:26:49,190 --> 00:26:51,850
You're probably not in a position to laugh at me.

419
00:26:59,070 --> 00:27:00,470
Anyone wants some juice?

420
00:27:01,110 --> 00:27:02,000
- I'll get it. - I'll get it.

421
00:27:02,000 --> 00:27:03,230
No, no, no, I'll go.

422
00:27:05,350 --> 00:27:06,880
- Stay here. - Stay here.

423
00:27:09,110 --> 00:27:10,880
Waiter, a glass of juice please.

424
00:27:10,880 --> 00:27:12,070
What kind of juice would you like?

425
00:27:12,070 --> 00:27:13,530
- Blueberry. - Blueberry.

426
00:27:14,830 --> 00:27:15,710
Hot or cold?

427
00:27:15,880 --> 00:27:16,800
- Cold. - Cold.

428
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:19,800
And sweetness?

429
00:27:19,950 --> 00:27:21,950
- Full sweetness. - Full sweetness.

430
00:27:26,110 --> 00:27:27,110
One cup?

431
00:27:27,590 --> 00:27:28,590
One cup each.

432
00:27:29,280 --> 00:27:31,680
I'll pay for mine, and he pay by himself.

433
00:27:32,400 --> 00:27:33,430
Okay.

434
00:27:43,590 --> 00:27:44,590
Thank you.

435
00:27:51,070 --> 00:27:53,710
This is too much. I can't drink this much.

436
00:28:04,680 --> 00:28:06,400
Xianxian, you must be hungry.

437
00:28:06,640 --> 00:28:08,590
What about have a dinner together before we go back?

438
00:28:08,590 --> 00:28:09,470
Okay.

439
00:28:11,110 --> 00:28:12,880
Mr. Su, you treated me last time.

440
00:28:12,880 --> 00:28:14,340
I feel quite embarrassed.

441
00:28:14,350 --> 00:28:15,470
I'll pay this time.

442
00:28:16,190 --> 00:28:17,590
I haven't said yes yet.

443
00:28:17,590 --> 00:28:18,430
Sure.

444
00:28:18,950 --> 00:28:20,610
Why don't we call up everyone?

445
00:28:20,920 --> 00:28:23,040
We haven't had dinner together yet in the Huai City, anyway.

446
00:28:23,040 --> 00:28:24,880
I know a place that is quite good.

447
00:28:25,470 --> 00:28:26,560
However,

448
00:28:27,110 --> 00:28:29,370
Mr. Zhou, I'm afraid it's gonna cost you.

449
00:28:30,110 --> 00:28:31,400
Don't worry about me.

450
00:28:31,710 --> 00:28:32,970
You should worry about

451
00:28:33,040 --> 00:28:35,560
whether you stand a chance anymore.

452
00:28:39,950 --> 00:28:40,920
Too sour.

453
00:28:49,560 --> 00:28:50,640
See you around.

454
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:02,830
You're back.

455
00:29:06,350 --> 00:29:07,230
What is this?

456
00:29:07,590 --> 00:29:08,590
Blueberry juice.

457
00:29:09,000 --> 00:29:10,680
No, thanks. It's too sour.

458
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:15,950
Rumors had it, two cute guys

459
00:29:16,040 --> 00:29:17,970
went for you at the same time today.

460
00:29:18,280 --> 00:29:19,470
Tell me tell me,

461
00:29:19,760 --> 00:29:22,160
are you super happy today?

462
00:29:22,680 --> 00:29:23,880
How is that possible?

463
00:29:24,160 --> 00:29:25,640
They are two big babies!

464
00:29:26,110 --> 00:29:27,680
I am so annoyed.

465
00:29:30,040 --> 00:29:31,400
Anyway,

466
00:29:31,760 --> 00:29:35,310
I'm still rooting the CP of you and Zhou Siyue.

467
00:29:36,070 --> 00:29:38,400
You liked him for so many years.

468
00:29:39,040 --> 00:29:41,470
If you can't be together,

469
00:29:42,590 --> 00:29:44,400
it'd be such a huge shame.

470
00:29:46,040 --> 00:29:47,190
Actually,

471
00:29:48,830 --> 00:29:51,030
he asked me If I would be his girlfriend.

472
00:29:51,830 --> 00:29:54,470
I almost said yes.

473
00:29:55,880 --> 00:29:57,230
You refused?

474
00:29:57,400 --> 00:29:59,040
I liked him for so many years.

475
00:29:59,350 --> 00:30:01,470
And he's only been after me for a few days.

476
00:30:01,470 --> 00:30:03,470
If I just say yes so easily,

477
00:30:03,680 --> 00:30:04,680
I'll be completely controlled by him

478
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:05,920
in the future.

479
00:30:06,400 --> 00:30:07,330
You have a point.

480
00:30:11,040 --> 00:30:12,040
But,

481
00:30:12,470 --> 00:30:14,800
I always feel that something is missing

482
00:30:15,070 --> 00:30:16,560
between the two of us.

483
00:30:17,110 --> 00:30:18,280
What is missing?

484
00:30:19,190 --> 00:30:20,190
I don't know.

485
00:30:20,830 --> 00:30:22,560
I can't figure it out.

486
00:30:27,230 --> 00:30:28,000
Is she going?

487
00:30:29,590 --> 00:30:31,800
It's his treat this the evening.

488
00:30:32,160 --> 00:30:33,190
Are you going?

489
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:36,310
Forget it. I'm not.

490
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:38,190
Come now!

491
00:30:39,640 --> 00:30:40,950
I'll go out for a while.

492
00:30:52,590 --> 00:30:53,470
Bocong,

493
00:30:54,640 --> 00:30:56,040
why didn't you go inside?

494
00:30:56,230 --> 00:30:57,830
I want to tell you something.

495
00:30:58,350 --> 00:30:59,590
What is it?

496
00:31:00,070 --> 00:31:01,070
Here's the thing.

497
00:31:01,590 --> 00:31:03,250
I know that you like Ding Xian.

498
00:31:03,520 --> 00:31:04,470
I can help you.

499
00:31:07,470 --> 00:31:08,800
Why are you helping me?

500
00:31:10,430 --> 00:31:11,680
For Zhou Siyue?

501
00:31:13,280 --> 00:31:15,110
Well, they're not together yet.

502
00:31:15,310 --> 00:31:17,040
I still have a chance. So do you.

503
00:31:25,710 --> 00:31:26,350
Lou Feng,

504
00:31:26,350 --> 00:31:28,470
did you forget something again?

505
00:31:28,470 --> 00:31:29,470
You're so...

506
00:31:33,110 --> 00:31:34,350
Why are you here?

507
00:31:34,920 --> 00:31:36,310
To take you to dinner.

508
00:31:36,470 --> 00:31:37,430
I'm not hungry.

509
00:31:45,400 --> 00:31:47,470
You don't want to see me?

510
00:31:48,160 --> 00:31:50,920
Don't flatter yourself.

511
00:31:53,070 --> 00:31:55,670
I'm buying dinner for everyone because of you.

512
00:31:55,800 --> 00:31:58,280
I can't believe you're not even coming.

513
00:31:58,880 --> 00:32:01,040
I didn't ask for that.

514
00:32:01,680 --> 00:32:04,190
Anyway, I'll starve myself here if you won't go.

515
00:32:04,190 --> 00:32:05,230
I'm not leaving.

516
00:32:07,560 --> 00:32:08,830
Fine, I'll go.

517
00:32:09,350 --> 00:32:10,230
I'll go eat.

518
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:17,160
Welcome!

519
00:32:18,680 --> 00:32:19,470
Xianxian.

520
00:32:19,800 --> 00:32:20,400
Here.

521
00:32:20,560 --> 00:32:22,760
Xianxian, this way, I saved you a seat.

522
00:32:23,280 --> 00:32:23,950
Okay.

523
00:32:24,350 --> 00:32:25,640
Zhou Siyue, sit here.

524
00:32:28,680 --> 00:32:29,680
Boss, here.

525
00:32:31,760 --> 00:32:32,760
I'm telling you,

526
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:34,720
we've been here for so many days,

527
00:32:34,760 --> 00:32:36,800
and didn't get the chance to get together, right?

528
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:38,640
Today, my boss pays the bill.

529
00:32:38,830 --> 00:32:40,680
Just order anything you want, cheers!

530
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:41,830
Okay, thank you, Prince Charming.

531
00:32:41,830 --> 00:32:43,110
You're welcome.

532
00:32:43,280 --> 00:32:44,760
Just enjoy yourself.

533
00:32:44,950 --> 00:32:46,150
Here, order the food.

534
00:32:52,070 --> 00:32:53,640
Thank you.

535
00:32:57,310 --> 00:32:58,590
I want this.

536
00:32:59,800 --> 00:33:01,830
Thank you, handsome.

537
00:33:03,190 --> 00:33:05,280
Nice that we're together here today.

538
00:33:05,560 --> 00:33:06,590
Let's not just eat.

539
00:33:06,590 --> 00:33:07,990
How about playing a game?

540
00:33:08,110 --> 00:33:10,430
Which game? Just the one we used to play.

541
00:33:10,430 --> 00:33:11,710
The King game.

542
00:33:11,920 --> 00:33:13,380
I brought the cards. Here.

543
00:33:13,470 --> 00:33:15,680
You are all prepared.

544
00:33:15,680 --> 00:33:16,520
Of course.

545
00:33:17,590 --> 00:33:18,850
Do you know how to play?

546
00:33:19,000 --> 00:33:19,880
I don't know.

547
00:33:20,110 --> 00:33:21,110
Here, I'll deal.

548
00:33:21,280 --> 00:33:22,740
It's okay. I'll teach you.

549
00:33:25,830 --> 00:33:26,830
Pass it on.

550
00:33:27,680 --> 00:33:29,430
First hand, who's the king?

551
00:33:30,950 --> 00:33:32,070
I am the king.

552
00:33:32,760 --> 00:33:34,000
My order is simple.

553
00:33:34,280 --> 00:33:36,400
Give me a toast, and call me gorgeous.

554
00:33:36,640 --> 00:33:37,560
That'll do.

555
00:33:37,760 --> 00:33:39,190
Who do you want? Right. What's the number?

556
00:33:39,190 --> 00:33:41,320
What's the number? What's the number?

557
00:33:41,560 --> 00:33:42,430
Number two.

558
00:33:42,560 --> 00:33:45,110
Number two. Who's number two? Who's number two?

559
00:33:45,110 --> 00:33:46,110
Who is number two?

560
00:33:53,310 --> 00:33:54,350
Gorgeous, to you.

561
00:33:54,760 --> 00:33:55,950
What? I can't hear you.

562
00:33:55,950 --> 00:33:56,760
What?

563
00:33:57,830 --> 00:33:59,760
Ban Jiayu, sorry.

564
00:34:00,110 --> 00:34:02,560
You gorgeous, here to you!

565
00:34:04,110 --> 00:34:05,590
Drink it up! Up, up.

566
00:34:06,880 --> 00:34:08,139
Drink up. You're good.

567
00:34:12,840 --> 00:34:13,870
Well done.

568
00:34:13,870 --> 00:34:14,760
Nice.

569
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:16,429
Go on, go on.

